
                         A 10MHz Frequency Counter.
                         --------------------------


    System Requirements Are, (Minimum In Brackets):-
    ------------------------------------------------

    1) A standard AMIGA A1200, (an A500+ or A600 for reduced capability).
    2) Workbench 3.0x, (Workbench 2.0x).
    3) AGA, (ECS).
    4) A PAL/NTSC monitor, (a PAL/NTSC television set).
    5) A hard disk drive, (a floppy disk drive).
    6) The mouse is MANDATORY.
    7) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 1.3x or less.
    8) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 3.1x or greater.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    General Information:-
    ---------------------

    This tool is a 10MHz Frequency Counter in two ranges, 100Hz to 100KHz
    direct and 10KHz to 10MHz using a simple prescaler.

